"acchiddehi asabalehi akammāsehi bhujissehi viññuppasatthehi aparāmaṭṭhehi "
"samādhisaṃvattanikehi."
msgstr ""
"It’s good to have the ethical conduct that’s loved by the noble ones, "
"unbroken, impeccable, spotless, and unmarred, liberating, praised by "
"sensible people, not mistaken, and leading to immersion."

msgctxt "sn40.10:11.2"
msgid ""
"Ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgamanahetu kho, devānaminda, evam’idhekacce sattā "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjantī”ti."
msgstr ""
